\[f_{\phi(\theta)}(x)=\mathbf{W}_{2}P^{\top}\sigma(P\mathbf{W}_{1}x)=\mathbf{W}_{2 }P^{\top}P\sigma(\mathbf{W}_{1}x)=\mathbf{W}_{2}\sigma(\mathbf{W}_{1}x)=f_{ \theta}(x),\] (1)

